dct_title_s: The north coast of Russia from the latest discoveries
dct_description_sm: Abstract: Map of the Russian Arctic emphasizing the northern coastline.

Notes: Detached from: The gentleman's magazine, and historical chronicle. Volume XIX : for the year M.DCC.XLIX. London : Printed by Edw. Cave, 1749. Originally published in the June 1749 issue, following page 248.
Includes pages 249-250 from the June 1749 issue of Gentleman's magazine, on a separate sheet.
Includes four illustrations relating to text on pages 249-250 of the magazine.
